Photo: Facebook“They do not realise that drinking too much can lead to serious health problems,” she said.She said youngsters also ended up in unnecessary debt because they spend all their money on booze.“The consequences of drinking have a negative impact on all of us,” she said.She said people who started drinking while young were more likely to drink to excess.
